headline: Intuit and Rehmann Partner to Fuel Mid-Market Business Growth with Powerful AI-Native ERP Solution and Advisory Services
summary: MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif. & TROY, Mich., November 17, 2025--Intuit Inc. (Nasdaq: INTU), the global financial technology platform that makes Intuit TurboTax, Credit Karma, QuickBooks, and Mailchimp, today announced a partnership with Rehmann, a professional advisory firm focused on accelerating client growth, to deliver Intuit Enterprise Suite to the firm’s growing list of scaling, mid-market businesses needing a powerful, AI-native, ERP solution that drives growth.
